725655f-a.title: Queens: 79th Street - 31st Avenue
725655f-a.text:
79th Street east side, between Thirty-first annd Thirty.
second Avenues. This house when Trains Meadow Road was in
existent was at the N.E. corner of the last mentioned Road
and 79th Street. The house formerly of frame was owned by
J. Peterson in 1873 and Mrs. Obell in 1896.
April 192S.
Fiugene L. Armbruster Collection
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
